Package: enrichit
Title: Gene Set Over-Representation Enrichment Analysis
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Panwen", "Wang", email = "pwwang@pwwang.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for gene set enrichment analysis using Fisher's exact test
    and a combined score approach that takes into account the expected rank distribution
    of gene sets. The package allows parsing of GMT files and performing over-representation
    analysis with robust statistical evaluation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    stats,
    digest,
    qvalue,
    rlang
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
LazyData: true
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
